{"arkId":"cl010096650","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010096650","modified ":"2025-12-12","title":"Statue f\u00e9minine \u00e9questre servant d\u0027aigui\u00e8re : Cl\u00e9lie sur son cheval","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Statue f\u00e9minine \u00e9questre servant d\u0027aigui\u00e8re : Cl\u00e9lie sur son cheval"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1595 - 1605","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 527 - Adolphe Rothschild, Vitrine 3","room":"Salle 527, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1595,"endYear":1605,"imprecision":"vers","text":"Fin du XVIe si\u00e8cle - d\u00e9but du XVII\u00e8 si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Lencker, Christoph","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MR 485","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statuette ; orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Ce groupe est compos\u00e9 d\u0027un grand cheval cabr\u00e9 mont\u00e9 par une cavali\u00e8re en amazone qui regarde vers l\u0027arri\u00e8re et tend son bras gauche dans la m\u00eame direction. La cavali\u00e8re, partiellement d\u00e9nud\u00e9e, porte une robe pliss\u00e9e laissant ses jambes d\u00e9couvertes. Sa coiffure tr\u00e8s \u00e9labor\u00e9e et dor\u00e9e, les bijoux \u00e9maill\u00e9s qu\u0027elle porte autour du cou et aux bras, tout comme la ciselure pr\u00e9cise des motifs de sa robe, compl\u00e8tent ce portrait raffin\u00e9 d\u0027une cavali\u00e8re represent\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u0027antique. Le cheval, dont la robe est minutieusement cisel\u00e9e, est dot\u00e9 d\u0027un arnachement d\u0027un \u00e9gal raffinement. Une puissante gerbe d\u0027eau jaillit au-devant du cheval et s\u0027\u00e9l\u00e8ve \u00e0 l\u0027oblique sous les pattes ant\u00e9rieures et le poitrail, sugg\u00e9rant la vitesse et la puissance de la course. L\u0027ensemble est dor\u00e9, \u00e0 l\u0027exception des chairs et du visage de la cavali\u00e8re.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Augsbourg, 1605-1610 ; ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre CL pour Christoph Lencker.","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"36,5","displayDimension":"36,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Longueur","value":"31","displayDimension":"31 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"10,5","displayDimension":"10,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Argent en partie dor\u00e9 et \u00e9maill\u00e9\r\nMat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Augsbourg = Ausgburg (Allemagne-\u003EBavi\u00e8re)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"D\u00e9pos\u00e9 au mus\u00e9e par l\u0027h\u00f4tel des monnaies, 22 novembre 1802 ; ancien fonds du mus\u00e9e, 1809 ; inventori\u00e9 dans les salons de l\u0027imp\u00e9ratrice Marie-Louise \u00e0 Compi\u00e8gne en 1810.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"ancien fonds","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value"